---
import MainLayout from '@/layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="GM Shrek Privacy Policy for MouseBoost, OmniReader, and OmniZip.">
  <section class="privacy-section">
    <h1 class="privacy-title">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="privacy-update">Last updated: May 2025</p>
    <p>
      This Privacy Policy explains how GM Shrek ("we", "our", or "us") collects, uses, and protects your information when you use our macOS applications: <b>MouseBoost</b>, <b>OmniReader</b>, <b>OmniZip</b>, <b>Pinwheel Browser</b> and so on (the "Apps").
    </p>

    <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><b>Personal Data:</b> Our Apps do <b>not</b> require you to create an account or provide personal information to use core features.</li>
      <li><b>Usage Data:</b> We may collect anonymous usage statistics (such as feature usage frequency, crash reports, or error logs) to improve our products. This data does not identify you personally.</li>
      <li><b>Files & Content:</b> All files you open, read, compress, or decompress with our Apps are processed locally on your device. We do <b>not</b> upload, store, or access your files on our servers.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>2. How We Use Information</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>To improve app stability, performance, and user experience.</li>
      <li>To fix bugs and respond to user feedback.</li>
      <li>To develop new features based on anonymous usage trends.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. Third-Party Services</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Some features (such as AI-powered reading in OmniReader) may allow you to connect to third-party AI services or APIs. Your use of such services is subject to their respective privacy policies.</li>
      <li>Our Apps may include links to external websites (e.g., App Store, GitHub Issues, QQ group). We are not responsible for the privacy practices of these third parties.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>4. Data Security</h2>
    <p>
      We take reasonable measures to protect your information. All file processing is done locally on your device. We do not collect or store your personal files.
    </p>

    <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>You may contact us at any time to inquire about your data or request deletion of any information you have voluntarily provided (e.g., via feedback email).</li>
      <li>You may opt out of anonymous analytics (if applicable) in the app settings.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>6. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>
      We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated date.
    </p>

    <h2>7. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>
      If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our Apps, please contact us at:
      <br />
      <a href="mailto:gmshrekhelp@outlook.com" class="privacy-link">gmshrekhelp@outlook.com</a>
      <br />
      Or open an issue on our GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/gmshrek/info/issues" class="privacy-link" target="_blank">gmshrek/info/issues</a>
    </p>
  </section>

  <style>
    .privacy-section {
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 3rem auto 0 auto;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 24px 0 rgba(60,60,120,0.08);
      padding: 2.5rem 2rem 2rem 2rem;
      color: #222;
      font-size: 1.08rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .privacy-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
      color: #222;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .privacy-update {
      color: #888;
      font-size: 0.98rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .privacy-section h2 {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
      color: #409EFF;
    }
    .privacy-link {
      color: #409EFF;
      text-decoration: underline;
      word-break: break-all;
    }
    .privacy-section ul {
      margin-left: 1.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    }
    .privacy-section li {
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
  </style>
</MainLayout>